    <node id="source2.Lab_Registry">
      <data key="d0">source2.Lab_Registry</data>
      <data key="d1">TABLE</data>
      <data key="d2">The Lab_Registry.csv table contains records of laboratory assays, including assay identifiers (`assays_ss_d`, `assays_dc_d`), types (`assays_ss_tst_tp`), creation details (`assays_crtd_b`), chemical identifiers (`assays_chmbl_d`), cell fractions (`assays_ss_sbclllr_frctn`), regions (`assays_ss_rgnsm`), cell types (`assays_ss_cll_tp`), relationships (`assays_rltnshp_tp`), and various measurements such as concentrations (`assays_ss_tx_d`), distribution levels (`assays_cll_d`), and test substance doses (`assays_tss_d`). Confidence scores (`assays_cnfdnc_scr`) and format types (`assays_b_frmt`) are also recorded.</data>
      <data key="d3">UNKNOWN</data>
      <data key="d4">custom_kg</data>
      <data key="d5">1773650711</data>
