      <data key="d1">TABLE</data>
      <data key="d2">The Krug.csv table contains genomic and clinical data for various samples, including identifiers, tumor characteristics, proteogenomic statuses, mutation types, and mutation statuses for key genes. It includes columns for sample IDs, tumor stage, ischemia time, PAM50 and NMF cluster classifications, and various scores related to tumor purity and immune/stromal activity.</data>
